  "text": "For the general cultivation of E.coli, strains were grown in LB broth supplemented with kanamycin (50ug ml -1 ), or chloramphenicol (30ug ml -1 ) as appropriate. Growth on solid medium contained 1.5% agar added to LB. Where noted, MOPS EZ Rich Defined Medium Kit (Teknova) was used in place of LB [CITATION_1] . Cysteine solutions were prepared immediately before use, as needed.",
